ries, putting into question the institutional character of medium ontology.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 4aFilm Studies. 4aFilm, Media, and Communication. 4aMedia Studies. 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / Direction & Production.2bisacsh  aCinema, curating, materiality, projection, new media.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066152108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2019z9783110605785oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2019 Englishz978311061001708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9789048527540zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048527540423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048527540/original  a978-3-11-061001-7  EBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-066152-1  Amsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2019  aZDB-23-DPKb2019